{"_id":"fvcAtgJJdxub8J5r","name":"Spell Resistance","content":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<h3>Armor Enchantment</h3>\n<p>The wearer gains the benefits of minor @Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Arcane Protection]{arcane protection}.</p>\n<p><strong>Enchantment Points:</strong> 4</p>\n<p><strong>Cost:</strong> 16,000 gp.</p>\n<p><strong>Craft:</strong> <em>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Arcane Protection]{Arcane protection}</em></p>\n</div>","img":"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/5f43f8ea1a91d63438d13159/artwork/icons/logo-eberron-circle-black.webp","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_d6wak2736pv","path":"Savage Eberron Rules#/CF_SEP/4. Magic Items#/CF_SEP/6.1. Enchantments","color":"#000000"},"journal-links":{"references":{}}}}
{"_id":"g2A86EK2kvFn6C6d","name":"Merchant","content":"<p>Merchants earn their living by buying and selling the works of others. Perhaps working for a dragonmarked house, an independent business, or just for yourself. They help establish company trade routes, negotiate prices, and ensure goods head where they’re needed.</p>\n<p><strong>Skills:</strong> Common Knowledge, Notice, Persuasion</p>\n<p><strong>Hindrance:</strong> Something</p>\n<p><strong>Background Edges:</strong> Charismatic</p>\n<p><strong>Combat Edges:</strong> Something</p>\n<p><strong>Leadership Edges:</strong> Something</p>\n<p><strong>Power Edges:</strong> Something</p>\n<p><strong>Professional Edges:</strong> Something</p>\n<p><strong>Social Edges:</strong> Something</p>\n<p><strong>Weird Edges:</strong> Scavenger</p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"flags":{"journal-links":{"references":{}},"core":{"sourceId":"JournalEntry.jxNfRTYaBJROlyxo"},"cf":{"id":"temp_pkglbsbzxv","path":"Savage Eberron Rules#/CF_SEP/1. Character Creation#/CF_SEP/1.2. Character Concepts","color":"#000000"}}}
{"_id":"gaP0zf6waEQzXWLZ","name":"Mighty Cleaving","content":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<h3>Two-handed Melee Weapon Enchantment</h3>\n<p>The user gains the @Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-edges.Sweep]{Sweep} Edge.</p>\n<p><strong>Enchantment Points:</strong> 2</p>\n<p><strong>Cost:</strong> 10,000 gp.</p>\n<p><strong>Craft:</strong> —</p>\n</div>","img":"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/5f43f8ea1a91d63438d13159/artwork/icons/logo-eberron-circle-black.webp","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_d6wak2736pv","path":"Savage Eberron Rules#/CF_SEP/4. Magic Items#/CF_SEP/6.1. Enchantments","color":"#000000"},"journal-links":{"references":{}}}}
{"_id":"gg8nWrfCOyKklxit","name":"Travel Domain","content":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<div class=\"section-header\">\n<h1>Travel Domain</h1>\n</div>\n<div>\n<ul class=\"red-bullet-list\">\n<li><strong>Aspects:</strong> Travel, wanderlust, wilderness, messengers</li>\n<li><strong>Deities:</strong> Kol Korran, The Traveler</li>\n<li><strong>Available Powers:</strong>\n<div class=\"available-powers\">\n<p>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Arcane Protection]{Arcane Protection}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Augury]{Augury}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Beast Friend]{Beast Friend}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Bolt]{Bolt}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Boost/Lower Trait]{Boost/Lower Trait}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Burrow]{Burrow}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Conjure Item]{Conjure Item}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Damage Field]{Damage Field}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Darksight]{Darksight}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Deflection]{Deflection}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Detect/Conceal Arcana]{Detect/Conceal Arcana}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Disguise]{Disguise}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Dispel]{Dispel}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Divination]{Divination}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Entangle]{Entangle}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Environmental Protection]{Environmental Protection}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Farsight]{Farsight}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-power