>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-edges.Adaptable Caster]{Adaptable Caster}</td>\n<td>S, AB (Artificer, Magic, or Wizard), arcane skill d6</td>\n<td>The trappings can be changed on the powers for 1 Power Point.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-edges.Arcane Armor]{Arcane Armor}</td>\n<td>N, Arcane Interference</td>\n<td>Your Armor Interference counts as one level higher.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-edges.Channeling]{Channeling}</td>\n<td>S, AB</td>\n<td>Reduce Power Point cost by 1 with a raise on the @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Activation]{Activation} roll.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-edges.Concentration]{Concentration}</td>\n<td>S, AB (Any) or MP (Any)</td>\n<td>Double duration of all non-Instant powers.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-edges.Craft Arcane Device]{Craft Arcane Device}</td>\n<td>S, AB (Any but Psionics), Repair d6</td>\n<td>Allows user to create arcane devices to share with others imbued with a single power.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-edges.Finely Tuned]{Finely Tuned}</td>\n<td>S, Sm d8 Craft Arcane Device or Infuse Item, Repair d8</td>\n<td>Reduce the cost of creating @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Arcane Devices]{Arcane Devices}.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-edges.Holy/Unholy Warrior]{Holy/Unholy Warrior}</td>\n<td>S, AB (Any or MP (Any), Vow (to your Deity)</td>\n<td>Add +1 to +4 to @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Soak Rolls]{Soak Rolls} for each Power Point spent.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-edges.Mentalist]{Mentalist}</td>\n<td>S, AB (Psionics), Psionics d6</td>\n<td>+2 to opposed @Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Psionics]{Psionics} rolls.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-edges.New Powers]{New Powers}</td>\n<td>N, AB</td>\n<td>Your character knows two new powers.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-edges.Power Points]{Power Points}</td>\n<td>S, AB (Any) or MP (Any)</td>\n<td>Grants 5 additional Power Points.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-edges.Power Surge]{Power Surge}</td>\n<td>WC, N, AB (Any), arcane skill d8</td>\n<td>The hero recovers 10 Power Points when his action card is a Joker.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-edges.Soul Drain]{Soul Drain}</td>\n<td>S, Sp d8, AB (Any) or MP (Any)</td>\n<td>Take a level of @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Fatigue]{Fatigue} to recover 5 Power Points, or 2 to recover 10.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<table class=\"table summary-table\"><caption class=\"table-caption\">\n<h2 class=\"table-title\">Professional Edges</h2>\n</caption>\n<thead>\n<tr class=\"table-header-row\">\n<th class=\"table-column-header\">Edge</th>\n<th class=\"table-column-header\">Requirements</th>\n<th class=\"table-column-header\">Summary</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-edges.Ace]{Ace}</td>\n<td>N, A d8</td>\n<td>Character may spend @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Bennies]{Bennies} to @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Soak Rolls]{Soak} damage for his vehicle and ignores up to 2 points of penalties.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-edges.Acrobat]{Acrobat}</td>\n<td>N, A d8, Athletics d8</td>\n<td>Free reroll on acrobatic @Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Athletics]{Athletics} attempts.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"improved-edge\">@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-edges.Combat Acrobat]{Combat Acrobat}</td>\n<td>S, Acrobat</td>\n<td>−1 to hit with @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Attacks]{ranged and 